---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Rank Labs">

<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-sm text-cyan-300 font-mono mb-4">OUR STORY</div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About <span class="gradient-text">Rank Labs</span></h1>

    <!-- Founder Story -->
    <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 mb-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
      <img src="/founders.jpg" alt="Josiah &amp; wife — founders of Rank Labs" class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-xl object-cover shrink-0" />
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Built by the people who needed it.</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Josiah is a Lead SRE Engineer at Disney, where he designs and builds the platforms
            that power Disney's AI integrations at scale.
          </p>
          <p>
            His wife runs <strong class="text-white">One Take Wonder Marketing</strong> — a marketing and media placement
            company that helps businesses grow. For years, she hired outside agencies to handle SEO
            for her clients. The results? Spotty at best. Inconsistent deliverables, vague reports,
            and pricing that never matched the output.
          </p>
          <p>
            So they built Rank Labs. Her marketing expertise defined what SEO success actually looks like.
            His platform engineering experience made it automated, consistent, and AI-driven.
            The result: a formula that covers everything SEO demands — and puts real updates
            in the hands of the customer, every single week.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Formula</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">
        Every site that enters the Rank Labs system goes through the same proven formula:
        crawl → analyze → optimize → create → repeat. AI handles the heavy lifting at every
        stage — crawling thousands of pages, identifying gaps, drafting content, and tracking
        rankings. You get the results without the agency overhead.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why a Lab?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">
        Agencies rely on manual processes. Manual processes are slow, inconsistent, and expensive.
        A lab runs experiments at scale. Our AI runs the equivalent of a full SEO team's weekly
        output — every single day — for $599/month.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">
        You still get human oversight and final approval on everything. The AI does the work.
        You make the calls. That's the formula.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
        {[
          { label: 'Hosting', value: 'Cloudflare Pages (Global Edge)' },
          { label: 'Crawler', value: 'Custom AI Crawler Engine' },
          { label: 'Content', value: 'LLM-Powered Research & Writing' },
          { label: 'Monitoring', value: 'Prometheus + Grafana' },
          { label: 'Deployment', value: 'GitOps with Argo CD' },
          { label: 'Infrastructure', value: 'Kubernetes (k3s)' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="text-xs text-cyan-400 mb-1">{item.label}</div>
            <div class="text-sm">{item.value}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Based in Florida</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">
        Proudly operating from the Sunshine State. We serve businesses across the US —
        from local shops to national brands.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
